Champaign.Alpha Gamma Delta Fraternity House: Alpha Gamma Delta (ΑΓΔ) is an international women's fraternity, founded on May 30, 1904, at Syracuse University. The fraternity promotes academic excellence, philanthropic giving, ongoing leadership and personal development and above all, a spirit of loving sisterhood. Also known as "Alpha Gam", Alpha Gamma Delta's current membership exceeds 189,000.
